| Criteria | Graviton | AMD | Intel |
|---------|----------|-----|------|
| Architecture | ARM64 | x86_64 | x86_64 |
| Cost | Lowest | Lower | Higher |
| Price/Performance | Excellent | Very Good | Good |
| Compatibility | Medium-High | High | Very High |
