# Best Use Cases

| Workload | Recommended Processor |
|---------|----------------------|
| Frontend | Graviton |
| APIs | Graviton / AMD |
| Middleware | AMD |
| Databases | AMD |
| Legacy Apps | Intel |
| Cost Sensitive Workloads | Graviton |

---

# Recommended Instance Selection

## Frontend Tier
Provisioning: ASG  
Processor: Graviton

```bash
t4g.medium
m7g.large
c7g.large
```

---

## Application Tier
Provisioning: ASG  
Processor: Graviton / AMD

```bash
m7g.large
c7g.large
m6a.large
c6a.large
```

---

## Middleware Tier
Provisioning: Manual  
Processor: AMD

```bash
Redis          r6a.large
Kafka          m6a.xlarge
Elasticsearch  r6a.xlarge
```

---

## Database Tier
Provisioning: Manual  
Processor: AMD

```bash
r6a.large
r6a.xlarge
```

---

## Legacy or Specialized
Provisioning: Manual  
Processor: Intel

Use only where:
- Vendor restrictions exist  
- Legacy compatibility required  
- Intel tuned workloads  

